message: Truckers Against Trafficking has been a huge help in fighting this horrible crime. Today, there are 440,000 truckers registered as TAT-trained. That means there are 440,000 men and women on the road who know how to spot and report suspicious activity that might be related to human trafficking. TAT has handed out over one million wallet cards that give reminders on all the things to look for if you think someone might be involved in trafficking.
